    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Despite its fearsome name, this technique is reasonably harmless. You gather Chakra in your palm and push it forward with force, shredding the target's clothing. Any piece of equipment that can be considered clothing, which includes fabric and plastic armor, is completely destroyed.<br><br>Leather equipment and mastercraft equipment is unaffected, as is more resilient gear.</p>\n\n\n\n",
